    "description": "Guide documentation",
    "content": "<p>Sometimes, words just aren't enough. Our server supports a wide range of custom emojis that you can use in chat to show exactly how you're feeling.</p>\n<h3>How to Use Emojis:</h3>\n<p>To see a full list of all available emojis and their codes, simply use the command:</p>\n<p><code>/emojis</code></p>\n<p>From there, you can copy and paste the emoji codes directly into your chat messages. Have fun with them!</p>\n",
